
USAGE: kibitz message

Sends your message to all the observers of a game.

' is an alias for kibitz (and so is "). Both end up in the game record.

If observing multiple games, you can specify the game number to direct
your kibitz to the correct game.  To kibitz to game 4, you would type:

     kibitz 4 c3 is a good move
or

     ' 4 c3 is a good move

SEE ALSO: censor observe

